title: Sky
alt: I dropped a bird and I didn't hear it hit bottom.
transcript:
[Megan approaches Beret Guy, who appears to be doing a handstand on the lawn.]
Megan: What are you doing?
Beret Guy: Clinging to the ceiling of a bottomless abyss.[Megan walks past him.]
Megan: You are very odd.[Megan towards a mailbox.][As she passes the mailbox, she looks up.][This panel appears to be upside down. Megan is clinging to the mailbox, and Ponytail approaches her.]
Ponytail: What's wrong?
Megan: I looked down.
